All Versions

  • Compare Networks: Fixed a bug in Volatility Map where only comparison networks were displayed
  • Compare Networks: Top Specialty Groups quadrant - graph correctly displays Market Penetration calculations
  • Zip codes: Fixed a bug causing an error when a valid zip code, which has no providers, is used in a search
  • Zip codes: Fixed a bug causing an error when zip codes had leading or trailing spaces
  • Zip codes: Fixed a bug causing an error when custom geography was used in location field
